text: Luis del Cerro (7 May 1924 - 30 April 2019) was a Spanish sport shooter who competed in the 1968 Summer Olympics, the 1972 Summer Olympics, the 1976 Summer Olympics and in the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Spanish male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Spain Category:Shooters at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Barcelona
title: Luis del Cerro
